
## Roewe RX8

The Roewe RX8 is a mid-size SUV produced by Roewe of SAIC group. It is the flagship SUV of the brand of Roewe, replacing the Roewe W5.

# Overview 

The Roewe RX8 debuted in April 2018, at the Beijing Auto Show. The Roewe RX8 comes in five and seven seat variants, and shares a shortened, but same platform with the Maxus D90 full size SUV, which is also a product under the SAIC group. 

